                            <h4 class="mb-3">Resource Description</h4>
                            <p>The United States Code Annotated (USCA) is a comprehensive legal resource providing an annotated and 
                            updated version of the United States Code. Developed by legal experts and scholars, the USCA offers in-depth
                             legal commentary, analysis, and annotations alongside the statutory text, making it an invaluable tool for 
                             legal practitioners, scholars, and researchers. </p>

