                            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                                <li><i class="fa fa-angle-right text-primary me-2"></i><strong>Legal Commentary</strong> : The USCA provides detailed legal commentary and analysis accompanying each section of the United States Code, offering insights into legislative intent, judicial interpretations, 
